      "value": "<p>You have a preternatural sense of danger and sometimes find your body reacting before your mind notices the risk.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Wis 17</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Once per day, if you would be unable to act in the surprise round because you failed a Perception check, you can still act on your initiative count in the surprise round, though you still have the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.MZ8OoH1GE9qDMyCD]{flat-footed} condition until you act on your turn in regular initiative.</p>"
